WEBVTT

00:00.090 --> 00:02.270
Misato-chan took a day off of school.

00:02.680 --> 00:06.480
I don’t think she’s completely alone, but I was sad for her.

00:07.040 --> 00:10.010
I left drawing class early because I was sad.

00:10.510 --> 00:12.760
I had Dad’s present that I wanted to give her.

00:13.390 --> 00:16.170
I hope Misato-chan comes to school tomorrow.
